Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The history of games can be traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the way to Ancient Egypt 5,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These ancient games decided the fate of the citizens and the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were called the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, the time where a boy has solved the Millennium Puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and released the Dark Games has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy with both a heart of light and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People refer to him as Yuugiou: The Game King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Yugi... Jounouchi-han.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinosaur Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Mai Kujaku's servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! Here's the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nightmare Shadow Sonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What happened? The Shadow Sonic was reflected!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Barbarian Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda's card helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful, Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(324,131)}Dark Fire! Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster in defense mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Barbarian Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two Barbarians powered each other up! Now there's a great chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Jounouchi! Show this dinosaur bastard the power of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power of friendship, was it? What bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ultimate card is still in my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Here it is! My ultimate card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very rare for someone to see this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, even if ya lose, you can still feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time that I've see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one, just like the Blue-Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..it's a legendary card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki had a card like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have traded almost all my cards for this super-rare card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use the magic card Dark Dragon Clan Claws\Nand give it a power up!{Yami Ryuuzoku no Tsume}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame Bullet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine and Honda's Barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strength of your friendship is so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can do it when you want, servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Jounouchi... it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... is there a way for Jounouchi to win? If this keeps up, he will lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this situation... The way for Jounouchi's victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can just think there's only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I promised that I wouldn't give any advice to Jounouchi-kun....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! An amateur like you beating {\i1}me{\i0} is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no more cards that can defeat Ryuzaki's monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will I lose here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it! There must be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in yourself, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! There's no way for you to defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah... Jounouchi set the Time Magician card on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can predict what happens when the Time Magic of the Time Magician card is used.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, I don't think that he knows that it can be used like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, servant! Finish him off quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... Mai Kujaku lost to this amateur thanks to the Time Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means that if I have the Time Magician I can't lose to Mai Kujaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this duel, what do you think about the winner getting one of the opponent's rare cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, I'll take your Time Magician....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of it... I played it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, if I lose, I'll give you the Red-Eyes card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing? Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki! I don't agree with this kind of condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my servant you have to obey my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who's{\i0} yer servant? Ye're annoyin' me! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on...? Red-Eyes is a super-rare card...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For him to bet it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Time Magician must...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}be more valuable than it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that I don't know what will happen if I play this card alone... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, Ryuzaki! In this duel, if I lose, I'll give you the Time Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that happens... I'll use this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He discovered it, didn't he? His only possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! He said too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait! The possibility to activate Time Magic is 1 in 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't you who decides for the Time Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Roulette!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roulette started to spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is good, it's Time Magic, otherwise it'll self-destruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Hit the good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pointer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In an instant, millions of years passed and Red-Eyes became a fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Red-Eyes was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki... as promised, give your star chips and Red-Eyes to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Jounouchi-kun won!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You... came back just to beat me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really worried me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this beating was obvious, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not so bad that I need for you to worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! Jounouchi-kun! Honda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them be, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way they show their gratefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...  they really are like Idiot number 1 and Idiot number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting dark already, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems there's no duelist in this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no duelist that would battle at night, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find a good place to spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really? This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... They invite us to a tournament where we have no meals... it's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Besides Yugi, not one of us was invited, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I don't care about star chips, I want food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like a bed to sleep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found some mushrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! That's poisonous for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do something like that, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... You are all together this time too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Did you come here to eat in front of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it, Jounouchi? Want to trade this chocolate for your star chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around! These star chips are my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a joke! A joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a duelist, I didn't feel that you would degrade to that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...This person really pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this...? We'll have a truce for tonight. We're all tired, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We've been dueling all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust her. Isn't she planning something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you don't want anything to eat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food and a tent, you have a little of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought all this for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duelist can only depend on himself. It's only natural to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking is your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, go get water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obeying that woman's order annoys me a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool... She's giving us food! Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Anzu-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shower over there, so, when they return with the water you can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that only girls can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Kujaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She seemed to be a annoying woman, but she has a good side...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boys! No peeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the food quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu-chan! I'll be on guard, so rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, why did you come to this island? It is really for the prize money?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a dealer on a cruise ship that traveled the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day, I met people with money that played cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These people only thought about money and power. These kind of people are stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I became fed up with that and started to hate people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always together with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? We're friends, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mysterious thing....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at you, I feel like I have lost something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a sound coming from the bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can we get in and see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san already has 8 star chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, you'll be the first one to get to the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, eventually we'll duel with each other, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can we forget about duels just for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Or we will not enjoy the food properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're together but tomorrow everyone will be enemies! That's to be a duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.... I'll take some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... That woman isn't cute at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To remember about the past.... I'm not like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Mai-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a really arrogant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, we will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I saw wasn't an illusion, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got on board too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't meet for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... we now have another supporter, so let's be grateful....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Everyone brought you their cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we are in the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... In this island everyone put their hearts in their cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the card you like the most, Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I am the Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... they are like kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what Jounouchi-kun said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, you too. What is the card you like the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, it's this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A weird woman that draws a lot of attention....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun, what is the card you like the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is, surely, Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I understand a little of everyone's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a card you like, gives you a feeling of believing in a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my grandpa says... cards have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you find the card's heart, the true duel can start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura-kun, which card do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Change of Heart card?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like a weird card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Yugi-kun.... Why not duel with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we won't bet any star chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that good Yugi? Since we got in this island we just had serious duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It would be good to duel without any pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you put your favorite cards in Yugi's deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's a good idea!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then let's get the cards from everyone and build an original deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All the preparations are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try your best, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi probably will win, but... Try your best too, Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Dark Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What complete fools you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this the Millennium Puzzle is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a Dark Game, I'll be your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have appeared... Other Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why is everyone doing cosplay of Duel Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Even me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Bakura-kun's power, we were sealed in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't win the game, we'll not be able to come back to the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that this is a dream! Guys, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Trap of the Metamorpot! Flame Swordsman{Honoo no Kenshi} in Danger
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
