Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:22:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
